<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .order-summary h2 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .order-summary p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .order-details table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .order-details th, .order-details td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .order-details th {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .total p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 5px 0;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .footer p {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your eLearning Order is Confirmed!</h1>
            <p>Thank you for your purchase. We're thrilled to have you onboard!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="order-summary">
            <h2>Order Details:</h2>
            <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= order._id %></p>
            <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= order.date %></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="order-details">
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Item</th>
                        <th>Quantity</th>
                        <th>Cost</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td><%= order.name %></td>
                        <td>1</td>
                        <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        
        <div class="total">
            <p><strong>Subtotal:</strong> $<%= order.price %></p>
            <p><strong>Total:</strong> $<%= order.price %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>.</p>
            <p>Thank you for choosing our platform!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
